mode: The Sapphire Motel is the perfect home base for your Bozeman adventure! Located just three blocks from downtown and a mile off I-90, we offer easy access to shops, restaurants, and outdoor activities. Enjoy competitive rates, top-notch service, and retro-inspired rooms with cozy beds and thoughtful amenities. Whether you're exploring or relaxing, we provide comfort, convenience, and a touch of nostalgia. Book today and make the Sapphire Motel your go-to spot in Bozeman!
